#

Zucchini and Corn Soup

30 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodLight Meal

Description

A creamy and comforting soup packed with fresh zucchini and sweet corn, perfect for a light meal.

Ingredients

  • zucchini: 2 medium, diced
  • corn (fresh or frozen): 1 cup
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • thyme (fresh or dried): 1 teaspoon
  • chives (for garnish): 2 tablespoons, chopped
